'''''Star Wars Insider'' 70''' is the seventieth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands in [[September]] [[2003]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk"
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Star News]]"
*"[[Best of Hyperspace]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]] and [[Paul Ens]]}}
*"[[HoloNet News (Insider)|HoloNet News]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
**"[[Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 14:9:04]]"
**"[[CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:9:15 Edition]]"
*"[[Gamescape]]" 
**"''Star Wars'' Galaxies Update" {{C|by [[W. Haden Blackman]]}}
**"[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy|Class Act]]" {{C|by [[Scott Steinberg]]}}
**"[[Galactic Campaign Guide|Galaxy Building 101]]" {{C|by [[Gary M. Sarli]]}}
*"[[Set Piece]]" &mdash; Padmé's Coruscant Apartment {{C|by [[Chris Trevas]]}}
*"[[Bookshelf]]" &mdash; Jack of Trades' New Essentials {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Comics Link]]" &mdash; Jedi vs. Jedi {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; But I Was Right... From a Certain Point of View! {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Toy Box]]" &mdash; The Clone Wars {{C|by Andy@Hasbro}}
*"[[Crossword (department)|Crossword]]" &mdash; Fantast-Rogation {{C|by [[Michael Selinker]]}}
*"[[Star Wars Q&A|''Star Wars'' Q&A'']] {{C|by Pablo Hidalgo}}
*"[[The Last Page]]" {{C|by [[Tony Moseley]]}}

===Features===
*"[[Prequel Update]]" {{C|by [[Dave Gross]]}}
*:<small>GWL is coming, look busy! Rick McCallum talks to ''Insider'' in the final days before shooting begins.</small>
*"[[Ray Park: The Face Behind Darth Maul]]" {{C|by [[Gabriela Tscharner-Patao]]}}
*:<small>The stuntman-turned-actor talks about his many face-obscuring roles, from [[Sith apprentice/Legends|Sith Apprentice]] to Iron Fist.</small>
*"[[Alienation: The Aliens of Episode II]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>[[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] introduced legions of new aliens to the ''[[Star Wars]]'' galaxy, from the keen-hearing [[Balosar (species)/Legends|Balosars]] to the spooky [[Umbaran/Legends|Umbarans]].</small>
*"[[Alien Faces: Stuart Freeborn on Star Wars Makeup Effects|Alien Faces: Stuart Freeborn on ''Star Wars'' Makeup Effects]]" {{C|by [[Ron Magid]]}}
*:<small>[[Stuart Freeborn]] gave aliens more than a new face in the movies-he gave them muscles, as well. Learn how the makeup maestro made the mighty [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] far more than an 8-foot ape.</small>
*"[[Hero of Cartao]]: Episode III Hero's End" {{C|by [[Timothy Zahn]]}}
*:<small>At last the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] show their true colors in the battle for [[Cartao/Legends|Cartao]].</small>

